    <item>
      <title>泰国最高法院将决定该国最受欢迎政党的命运</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/thai-court-set-to-decide-fate-of-thailand-s-most-popular-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国宪法法院将于周三作出裁决，决定该国最受欢迎的政党是否应因承诺修改有争议的王室诽谤法而违反选举规则而解散。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/thai-court-set-to-decide-fate-of-thailand-s-most-popular-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯任命辛瓦尔为政治领袖，停火希望渺茫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/hamas-says-leader-yahya-sinwar-will-also-become-political-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯任命 10 月 7 日袭击事件的幕后主谋叶海亚·辛瓦尔为其新政治领导人，这是对达成加沙停火协议的多边努力的最新打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/hamas-says-leader-yahya-sinwar-will-also-become-political-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 18:16:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国警方警告暴徒，周三将发生更多骚乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/uk-police-warn-rioters-as-more-unrest-planned-for-wednesday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国警方增派了警力，并表示如果极右翼活动分子按照网上流传的计划于周三晚聚集在移民中心，他们准备逮捕数百名极右翼活动分子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/uk-police-warn-rioters-as-more-unrest-planned-for-wednesday</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 16:53:01 GMT</pubDate>
